 for cultivation, as provided in subdivisions (a) to (c), inclusive, of Section 26060.1. For purposes of this paragraph, “cultivation” as used in Section 26060.1 shall have the same meaning as defined in Section 26001. The department shall consult with the State Water Resources Control Board and the Department of Fish and Wildlife in the implementation of this paragraph.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">(c) The applicant shall also provide a complete detailed diagram of the proposed premises wherein the license privileges will be exercised,
